organic.title: Samaritan Hematology & Oncology Consultants - Albany
organic.snippet: Samaritan Hematology & Oncology in Albany, OR offers cancer care including chemotherapy. Located at 1086 7th Ave SW Suite 200. Phone: 541-812-3330. Providers include Raed Benkhadra, MD and Robert Davis, MD.

organic.title: Samaritan Hematology & Oncology Consultants - Lebanon
organic.snippet: Samaritan Hematology & Oncology Consultants in Lebanon, OR, located at 525 N Santiam Hwy. Phone: 541-451-7462. Offers cancer care including chemotherapy. Providers include Raed Benkhadra, MD, and others.

organic.title: Medical Oncology & Hematology - Samaritan Health
organic.snippet: Samaritan Health offers medical oncology and hematology services, diagnosing and treating all cancers and blood disorders. Affiliated with Roswell Park, they provide clinical trials, telemedicine, and more. Located at 830 Washington Street, Watertown, NY.
